who take the condoms

21:28.983 --> 21:31.725
are the ones
who want to party.

21:31.725 --> 21:32.552
Oh!

21:32.552 --> 21:36.077
And party means sex.

21:36.077 --> 21:38.253
Anyone
want condoms?!

21:38.253 --> 21:40.647
Condoms suck.

21:40.647 --> 22:06.542
♪♪

22:06.542 --> 22:08.152
Uh, hey!
Miss!

22:08.152 --> 22:09.589
Hey, excuse me,
Miss!

22:09.589 --> 22:11.330
Oh, Miss.
Hey! Can I --

22:11.330 --> 22:13.767
Hey, I was
just wondering

22:13.767 --> 22:16.596
if I can offer you
a, uh, prophylactic?

22:16.596 --> 22:17.771
I'm sorry?

22:17.771 --> 22:20.208
Um, uh, it's slang
for a condom.

22:20.208 --> 22:23.646
We're giving them away to show
how the patriarchy is dying.

22:23.646 --> 22:26.693
You know,
it's almost dead.

22:26.693 --> 22:29.739
I mean,
we're white guys and --

22:29.739 --> 22:31.480
Do you know
who Karl Marx is

22:31.480 --> 22:33.526
'cause he would want you
to have one?

22:33.526 --> 22:35.049
Uh, thanks.

22:35.049 --> 22:36.659
No problem.

22:36.659 --> 22:38.008
Uh, just one
'cause we've got plenty,

22:38.008 --> 22:39.662
