22:39.662 --> 22:41.447
Hi.
Hi.

22:41.447 --> 22:44.580
So, um, the girls lacrosse team
just showed up at the booth,

22:44.580 --> 22:47.540
and, um...
we're out of bananas.

22:47.540 --> 22:49.237
Wha-- Like,
the lacrosse team?

22:49.237 --> 22:50.804
The girls
lacrosse team.

22:50.804 --> 22:53.807
