I-I'm joking.

23:25.534 --> 23:28.537
I-I'm working at
the stay safe booth over there.

23:28.537 --> 23:31.758
I-I'm just trying
to give back.

23:31.758 --> 23:32.802
I don't know.
I'm just doing my part.

23:32.802 --> 23:36.023
I like that.

23:36.023 --> 23:37.720
Hey, uh, Jake!

23:37.720 --> 23:39.722
Could I just borrow you
for one second?

23:39.722 --> 23:42.986
Yeah.

23:42.986 --> 23:45.467
I'm so sorry.

23:45.467 --> 23:48.731
I got to go, but,
um, yeah.

23:48.731 --> 23:50.994
It was a -- It was a pleasure
meeting you, Sandra.

23:56.217 --> 23:58.306
You know, um...
there's a party tonight

23:58.306 --> 24:00.003
at the Sig Delt house.

24:00.003 --> 24:01.570
We're throwing it.

24:01.570 --> 24:05.052
Uh, it's probably going to be
fun, so you should come.

24:05.052 --> 24:08.055
Yeah. Maybe.

24:08.055 --> 24:10.753
Maybe?

24:10.753 --> 24:13.277
Yeah, maybe is, uh --
maybe's great.

24:13.277 --> 24:16.977
Okay, well, uh, maybe
I'll see you there.

24:19.414 --> 24:21.851
['60s-era music playing]

24:21.851 --> 24:35.430
