25:10.944 --> 25:12.989
Something wrong? You've kind of
been acting a little weird

25:12.989 --> 25:14.774
ever since this morning?

25:14.774 --> 25:18.778
No, I'm fine. I'm just, uh...
yeah, I'm just laying low.

25:18.778 --> 25:20.562
Oh, yeah, that's cool.

25:20.562 --> 25:22.259
I'm laying low, too.

25:22.259 --> 25:24.392
You know, just laying real low
'cause I'm cool.

25:24.392 --> 25:26.133
We're cool.

25:26.133 --> 25:27.787
Oh, is
that girl coming?

25:27.787 --> 25:29.658
What?

25:29.658 --> 25:31.442
The girl
from this morning.

25:31.442 --> 25:33.793
I don't know, maybe.

25:33.793 --> 25:37.318
Cool. Maybe, who cares?
Whatever. You know.

25:37.318 --> 25:39.189
Whoa!
Hey, what is that?

25:39.189 --> 25:40.756
No! No! No!
Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!

25:40.756 --> 25:43.324
Oh, you dog!

25:43.324 --> 25:45.239
What?
Jenny Si--

25:45.239 --> 25:48.372
Jenny Simon, the head
of the history department?!

25:48.372 --> 25:52.463
Yeah, I had to brush up
on the cultural relevance

25:52.463 --> 25:54.335
of Mesopotamia
in the 21st century.

25:54.335 --> 25:56.119
How do you do it?

25:56.119 --> 25:57.991
I mean, you look good.
That's a given.

25:57.991 --> 25:59.558
There's something else.
It's --

25:59.558 --> 26:04.345
Carter, girls aren't
some complex puzzle

26:04.345 --> 26:05.607
that need
to be solved.

26:05.607 --> 26:07.087
They're the same
as you and me.

26:07.087 --> 26:08.523
